    "We explore different choices for α(•) in the supplementary.• <SOS> Token: ŝ = 1 -β(k)s + β(k)ϵ, ϵ ∼ N (0, I)Since autoregressive models prepend a special <SOS> token s to initialize the generation process, we also test injecting noise into s according to schedule β(•).Empirical Analysis.",
